- Use `st.cache_data` for expensive computations to improve performance
- Organize your app into multiple files using `st_pages` for better maintainability
- Implement proper error handling with `st.exception` for user-friendly error messages
- Use `st.set_page_config` to customize the page layout and appearance
- Leverage Streamlit components for interactive elements like charts and maps